        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 3–6. Peltoschema filicornis Reitter. 3) Venter of thorax and abdominal ventrite I with coxae removed; 4) male fore tibia and tarsus, latter rotated to show segment shape and planar view of claw; 5) tegmen and penis, dorsal and lateral view, showing outline of flagellum; 6) vaginal palpi and spermatheca." ;
